        h3 S̜w͚a̎r̍m̸
        p.subtext Realtime Electronics and Pipa, 2015
        p S̜w͚a̎r̍m̸ is an live-sampling instrument. It was originally built for the singular purpose of capturing live instrument input and playing it back as a drone. Here, that idea is extended to include other sound possibilities.
